        "value": "産物 — 米 九萬貳千七百拾九石四斗・茶 五十萬斤・蠟 八拾萬斤（但塊粉共）・索麺 百八萬斤・酒 壹萬三千九百八拾八石八斗・石炭 三千六百萬斤・陶器 貳萬俵餘・摺海老 四千五百五拾斤（原失：右之品々凡逐年增減有之候）"
      },
      {
        "purpose": "modern_jp_reading",
        "value": "産物（さんぶつ）— 当藩の主な産物と数量"
      },
      {
        "purpose": "english_translation",
        "value": "Products (sanbutsu), with quantities: rice 92,719 koku; tea 500,000 jin; wax 800,000 jin (incl. lump & powder); sōmen noodles 1,080,000 jin; sake 13,988 koku; coal 36,000,000 jin (Saga's renowned Hizen coalfields); ceramics 20,000+ bales (Arita/Imari porcelain); dried shrimp 4,550 jin. An editorial note records that these amounts fluctuate year to year (逐年增減有之候)."
      },
